divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b11e4f6 h2-title-on-light-bg elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b11e4f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Parents and Alumni Network Database<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-078c56f parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"078c56f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p dir=\"ltr\">An essential part of being an\u00a0<span class=\"il\">alumnus<\/span>\u00a0is finding ways to give back to the school through small acts of showing support.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">The first step is making sure that the school office has your contact details: E-mail address, Whatsapp numbers, or other ways you prefer to be contacted is the first start. Signing up to receive communications, opportunities to volunteer, or participating in events. If you want to sign up please complete this\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/form.jotformz.com\/61653868301660\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/url?q=https:\/\/form.jotformz.com\/61653868301660&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1712162565634000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3tSWBy_iNkWyNyrIMfEHvh\">form<\/a>:<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Being a resource to others is key for the\u00a0<span class=\"il\">Alumni<\/span>\u00a0Association success. There are many ways one can be a resource.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">1. Mentoring students and sharing some good advice that can reassure our students on academics, universities or living in cities abroad.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">2. Sharing job opportunities from your working place.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">3. Organising and participating in the yearly\u00a0<span class=\"il\">alumni<\/span>\u00a0reunion<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">4. Becoming the\u00a0<span class=\"il\">alumni<\/span>\u00a0representative for the Advisory Board (10 meetings of two hours per year).\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">5. Participating in the Virtual Professional Fair organised every year by our University Counselor to support our students who are deciding their career paths and universities.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">6. Internships. Be willing to support CGB students with some volunteer work at the company you are working for or within your field of activity, so that our students can get an insight into the working world. (One week)<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">7. Participating in Service Activities such as The Health Brigade or Building a House in Cazuca.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">8. Participating in Community Events such as Sports Championships, Alex Bjoroy tournament, Inter House Competitions, or the International Day.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">9. Promoting and collaborating with a\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/presentation\/d\/1dNH1Znh_Vk_xZ3BIr5tyNaPY47ejMsHyF7NmUUBhTC0\/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/url?q=https:\/\/docs.google.com\/presentation\/d\/1dNH1Znh_Vk_xZ3BIr5tyNaPY47ejMsHyF7NmUUBhTC0\/edit?usp%3Dsharing&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1712162565634000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3oB-Uf31qZiML8agAHNQBd\">CGB\u00a0<span class=\"il\">Alumni<\/span>\u00a0Newsletter\u00a0<\/a>\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">10. It could simply involve promoting your\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.cgb.edu.co\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/url?q=http:\/\/www.cgb.edu.co&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1712162565634000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0I0nEqE1EIeX1sLGu-dEGR\">school<\/a>, and spreading the word to other families.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Please contact\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:admissions@cgb.edu.co\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">admissions@cgb.edu.co<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7d62b3e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"7d62b3e\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8a87167 ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"8a87167\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9be9bd0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode\" data-id=\"9be9bd0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"shortcode.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shortcode\"><div class=\"_df_book df-container df-loading \" id=\"df_12042\"  title=\"cgb-alumni-newsletter\" _slug=\"cgb-alumni-newsletter\" wpoptions=\"true\" thumb=\"https:\/\/www.cgb.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cgb-alumni-newsletter.jpg\" thumbtype=\"bg\" ><\/div><script data-cfasync=\"false\">var option_df_12042 = {\"outline\":[],\"forceFit\":\"true\",\"autoEnableOutline\":\"false\",\"autoEnableThumbnail\":\"false\",\"overwritePDFOutline\":\"false\",\"direction\":\"1\",\"pageSize\":\"0\",\"source\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.cgb.edu.co\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2024\\\/04\\\/CGB-Alumni-Newsletter.pdf\",\"wpOptions\":\"true\"}; if(window.DFLIP && DFLIP.parseBooks){DFLIP.parseBooks();}<\/script><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\